---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Pest Control Insider — your trusted source for expert pest control content for professionals and homeowners.">
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 font-heading">Meet Kevin Larrabee</h1>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start mb-12">
        <img
          src="/author.jpg"
          alt="Kevin Larrabee"
          class="w-full sm:w-64 h-auto rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-sm flex-shrink-0"
        />
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">Kevin Larrabee</h2>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium mb-4">Pest Control Specialist &amp; Founder of Pest Control Insider</p>
          <p class="text-text leading-relaxed">
            Kevin Larrabee is a board-certified entomologist and licensed pest control operator with over 20 years of experience protecting homes and businesses from unwanted invaders. After earning his degree in entomology and completing advanced training in integrated pest management (IPM), Kevin spent a decade working as a field technician and technical director for one of the largest pest control companies in the Southeast. He launched Pest Control Insider to bridge the gap between professional-grade knowledge and the practical needs of homeowners dealing with everything from ants and termites to rodents and wildlife. Kevin holds certifications from the Entomological Society of America and is a frequent speaker at industry conferences. He lives in Florida, where the warm climate ensures he's never short of pest-related material.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">About Pest Control Insider</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-6">
          Pest Control Insider is a resource built for pest control professionals, exterminators, and homeowners who want reliable, expert-level information about pest identification, prevention, and treatment.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We believe that quality pest control knowledge should be accessible to everyone — whether you're a seasoned exterminator looking for the latest industry insights or a homeowner trying to identify and eliminate pests.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">What We Cover</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li>Pest identification guides and prevention strategies</li>
          <li>DIY pest control treatments and best practices</li>
          <li>Termite detection, treatment, and prevention</li>
          <li>Rodent control and exclusion techniques</li>
          <li>Bed bug treatment and eradication methods</li>
          <li>Seasonal pest control checklists and tips</li>
        </ul>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">For Professionals</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our technical articles provide in-depth coverage of pest control methods, product comparisons, and treatment protocols to help you serve your clients better and grow your business.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">For Homeowners</h2>
        <p>
          We break down complex pest control concepts into practical, actionable advice so you can protect your home and family from unwanted pests — whether you go DIY or hire a pro.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
